<div class="title">Healing a Heavy Experience</div>
<div class="substance">Ayahuasca</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Malachy&Exact=1">Malachy</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Malachy. "Healing a Heavy Experience: An Experience with Ayahuasca (exp80355)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Aug 21, 2009. erowid.org/exp/80355</div>

